<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - GoToursBooking</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Learn about GoToursBooking — our mission to connect travelers with the Kenyan coast and our team.">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/@phosphor-icons/web"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .about-hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 80px 24px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .about-hero h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .about-hero p {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .content-section {
            padding: 60px 40px;
            max-width: 1120px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .grid-story {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 60px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .story-img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .team-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 32px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .team-card {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .team-avatar {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <div class="header-top">
            <a href="index.html" class="logo">
                <i class="ph-fill ph-palm-tree"></i>
                <span style="color:var(--ocean-600)">GoToursBooking</span>
            </a>

            <button class="mobile-toggle" aria-label="Toggle navigation"><i class="ph ph-list"></i></button>

            <nav class="main-nav">
                <a href="index.html">Home</a>
                <a href="listing.html">Listings</a>
                <a href="about.html">About</a>
                <a href="host.html" class="host-link">Become a Host</a>
            </nav>

            <div class="user-menu">
                <div class="search-bar-pill" style="min-width: 200px; width: auto; padding: 8px 16px;">
                    <a href="index.html" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit; font-weight: 600;">Return Home</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div class="about-hero">
            <h1>We are GoToursBooking</h1>
            <p>Connecting travelers with the authentic beauty of the Kenyan Coast. From Swahili villas in Lamu to luxury
                apartments in Nyali.</p>
        </div>

        <img loading="lazy" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516026672322-bc52d61a55d5?q=80&w=2072&auto=format&fit=crop"
            style="width: 100%; height: 500px; object-fit: cover;" alt="Kenya Coast" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/1400x500?text=GoToursBooking'">

        <div class="content-section">
            <div class="grid-story">
                <div>
                    <h2 style="font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Our Mission</h2>
                    <p style="font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6;">
                        Founded in 2026, PwaniStays was built on a simple premise: the Kenyan coast offers some of the
                        most unique and beautiful hospitality experiences in the world, yet finding them was often
                        difficult.
                        <br><br>
                        We set out to create a platform that not only lists properties but celebrates the culture,
                        architecture, and warmth of the 'Pwani' (Coast) region. Our goal is to empower local hosts and
                        provide travelers with unforgettable stays.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <img loading="lazy" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1489749798305-4fea3ae63d43?q=80&w=2074&auto=format&fit=crop"
                        class="story-img" alt="Mission" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/800x600?text=GoToursBooking'">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-section" style="border: none;">
            <h2 style="font-size: 32px; text-align: center;">Meet the Team</h2>
            <div class="team-grid">
                <div class="team-card">
                    <img loading="lazy" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1531123897727-8f129e1688ce?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop"
                        class="team-avatar" alt="CEO" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/120x120?text=GT'">
                    <h3>Amani Juma</h3>
                    <p style="color:var(--text-secondary)">Founder & CEO</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-card">
                    <img loading="lazy" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506277886164-e25aa3f4ef7f?q=80&w=2135&auto=format&fit=crop"
                        class="team-avatar" alt="CTO" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/120x120?text=GT'">
                    <h3>David Kamau</h3>
                    <p style="color:var(--text-secondary)">Head of Engineering</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-card">
                    <img loading="lazy" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573497019940-1c28c88b4f3e?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop"
                        class="team-avatar" alt="Ops" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/120x120?text=GT'">
                    <h3>Sarah Hassan</h3>
                    <p style="color:var(--text-secondary)">Head of Operations</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-card">
                    <img loading="lazy" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500648767791-00dcc994a43e?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop"
                        class="team-avatar" alt="Design" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/120x120?text=GT'">
                    <h3>Brian Omondi</h3>
                    <p style="color:var(--text-secondary)">Lead Designer</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="site-footer">
        <div class="footer-container">
            <div class="footer-brand">
                <strong>GoToursBooking</strong>
                <p style="color:var(--text-secondary); margin-top:6px;">Discover the Kenyan Coast</p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a href="#">Privacy</a>
                <a href="#">Terms</a>
                <a href="#">Contact</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:center; margin-top:24px; color:var(--text-secondary);">© 2026 GoToursBooking Kenya, Inc.</div>
    </footer>
    <script src="main.js"></script>

</body>

</html>